    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 300ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[510ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and stir through your <strong>dried oregano </strong>– this is your<strong> herby stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your<strong> cannellini beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-7-1647949506594-x200.jpg",
