        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>herby stock</strong> and <strong>drained</strong> <strong>cannellini beans </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for a further 3 min</p>",
