    {
      "instruction": "<p>Tear your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces and add to a baking tray with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong>,<strong> </strong>a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 5-6 min or until crisp – these are your <strong>salt & pepper croutons</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
