        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the croutons are in the oven, drain then add your <strong>king</strong> <strong>prawns</strong> to the pot and cook for 4-5 min further or until cooked through – this is your <strong>Tuscan-style king prawn & cannellini bean soup</strong></p>",
